Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.86,0:00:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already summer vacation!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't made any progress whatsoever with Ichijou-kun yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand how you can be so spineless.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the help I gave you, after you got all those chances,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.12,0:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you possibly not make any progress?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.80,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.88,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd take the initiative to try asking him out yourself once in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.17,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not that I think you're capable of such a thing, Kosaki-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate, you'll never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Ruri-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.52,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the thing is, tomorrow...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.36,0:00:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited Ichijou-kun to my house.
