Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.35,0:01:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Onodera. What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a second?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.82,0:01:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.23,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you... have any plans this weekend?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.26,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free, by any chance?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Don't tell me she's about to ask me out!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.78,0:01:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is... I wanted to ask if you could take on a part-time job.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, it's just a job.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.87,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A job?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.74,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, one of our employees has an emergency and can't come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.50,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom said it'd be best to find someone who's a good cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.46,0:01:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, since you're the only one I know who can cook...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're interested...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.60,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here I was, thinking that I wouldn't be seeing Onodera for a while because of summer vacation...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never had a part-time job before,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but today I'm gonna show Onodera my good side!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.11,Sign2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnPainted\b1\c&H000000&\pos(511.111,246.889)\frx334\fry0}Japanese Sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.11,Sign2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnBrush Strokes\b1\c&H000000&\fscx200\fscy200\pos(578.667,333.333)\frx340}ONODERA
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.53,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sure haven't been to Japanese Sweets Onodera in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.16,0:02:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a single product in stock?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about it! Isn't that your job?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me? Make sure you have it by this evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head over there myself to pick it up later. Got that?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit... We should be okay as far as baked goods go,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but what am I going to do about the raw sweets?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a student doing in my shop?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go suck on a lollipop!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no... Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! That's him!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the temp!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaki...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming in today.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.23,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa... That uniform!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is one cute shopgirl!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.45,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.13,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering who it could be when you said you knew a great cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just one of your classmates?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, he's kind of a bean sprout.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.81,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What I was looking for was someone who I could throw to the dogs with no problem, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, the kitchen is a \Nprofessional's sacred realm.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To even think that a mere high school student can cook...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ichijou-kun's not like that at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.49,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that Ichijou-kun cooks his family's meals by himself, every single day!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're talking about a ton of food!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.42,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Enough for dozens of people, all by himself!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you whip something up, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll determine whether or not you're up to the job.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's no good, I'll send you packing. Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Just like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I did take a crash course in Japanese sweets,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that doesn't mean I can pass...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give it all you've got, Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, next is...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's wiping the condensation off the bowl to be thorough.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like he doesn't have a clue about Japanese sweets,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he's no newbie when it comes to cooking.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm done.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.89,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say your name was Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.21,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Marry my daughter!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, at first I wasn't so sure,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but you brought home a surprisingly worthy man, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichijou-kun's not really that kind of—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always spacing out, so I was starting to worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But this kid, he's got what it takes,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'll make a great heir to the family business, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk about it later.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can kind of trust him now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.92,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaki, show him how to make bean jam paste and the easiest sweets.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the shop till noon.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see your face when you're in front of a guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but to took this opportunity to introduce me to a guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My little Kosaki...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You. Little. Devil.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.07,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That mother of yours is something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive her.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, come with me. I'm going to show you some stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And next... You add some granulated sugar to this dough over here...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.47,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, Onodera, I can't believe you remember every little step.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you help out a lot, making stuff like this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.19,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't actually get to make anything. I'm pretty awful at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little, I've always thought it looked fun, so I watched.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably why.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.24,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they did let me try making some myself one time, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who ate my sweets ended up keeling over,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and the shop was shut down for three days!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's had her deadly touch forever, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one thing I did get praised for was my finishing touches,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.42,0:06:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and since I've been helping with that all this time, it's become my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm done mixing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this look about right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Just like that! It looks so yummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.51,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You perfect the taste, Ichijou-kun, and I'll perfect the shape.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That way we'll make some great Japanese sweets!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that just now? A proposal? \NY-You want me to marry into this family?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaki! I'm stepping out for a bit, so watch over the shop!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.84,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, just look at us now! Can you believe the great vibe we've got going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I almost want to stay here forever and start a family!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.43,0:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! So you're holding down the fort today, Kosaki-chan? Lucky me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Yoshino-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like your usual?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly have a good memory!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? How about we go on a date sometime, you and I?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! There you go again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.56,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your change comes out to 615 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around, Kosaki-chwan!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously! Flirting around like that at his age!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.62,0:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still go out on dates with Chitoge-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—Why would I go out with {\i1}her{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, sure we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we are going out and all...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ichijou-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you haven't heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.46,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you two aren't really boyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you... Since when?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoge-chan told me quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure that you already knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe that moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.48,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're gonna tell Onodera, then let me know, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.33,0:09:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichijou-kun never knew about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why he acted like he was in a relationship even when we were alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.94,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then, why would he hide that photo?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.05,0:09:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onodera knew all this time that we weren't dating?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold up. If that's the case...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.99,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then does that mean I'm in the clear to tell her how I feel about her now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.28,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no, hold on a second! No way it's that simple!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotta get the timing right too and all...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it's gotten really windy outside, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, they just said on the news that a typhoon was coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to come down.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting pretty heavy. I wonder if your mom is all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? This is Japanese Sweets Onodera.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.39,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she can't make it back because the weather's too bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And to look after the shop...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man. Well, I can understand why, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She also said...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be too dangerous for you to go home,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so I should have you stay the night.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.85,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wants me to stay the night? \NMe, spend the night at Onodera's?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.86,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... Onodera, isn't there anyone else home?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad had some business to take care of and won't be coming home.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My little sister lives in a dorm.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a little sister?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew that—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what am I saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this for real? A night alone with Onodera?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I really stay the night here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, no way! Of course I can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't just spend the night at a girl's house alone with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can I borrow an umbrella? I can handle a little drizzle on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The roof tiles are coming down!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! Better not wander around outside too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-How did this happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rather, how does Onodera feel right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's gotta be uneasy about this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do? I can't help but grin!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just knowing that we were going to work together was almost too much for me to handle!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.53,0:12:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? I can't stop my face from going slack!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.14,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You can't do this, Kosaki! You can't let him see you looking so pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come back! Come back, normal face!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so what do you think we should do, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... about dinner?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you smirking, Onodera?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.16,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There was this really funny TV show on yesterday,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I randomly remembered it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.49,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! What am I gonna do? I can't hide it at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it. She's probably nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I can't let myself panic.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just change the subject...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we talk it over and decide?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up to my room, and—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.12,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I really say something so audacious?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that? \NLetting me come up to your room?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course I am!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's n-nothing special, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.48,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait here a second. Let me tidy it up a little!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.34,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also want to change!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure! Don't rush on my account, okay? Just take your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to that! She's totally cleaning up.
