Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.71,Sign3,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnDaigoTai-W7\fax0.2\fscx70\fscy70\c&HD8E5D0&\bord0\frx8\fry8\frz12.54\pos(683,595)}Febreze
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will this do, I wonder?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guess I'll go with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm making him wait. I should hurry...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.38,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Thanks for waiting! You can come up now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never been in a girl's bedroom before.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.02,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who would've thought Onodera's would be the first?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make yourself at home, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is Onodera's room.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It's really cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it totally smells great, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be back with some tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.57,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bed that Onodera sleeps in every night...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The desk where she studies...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hell, this is where she just changed...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop imagining things like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll lose all sense of reason!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this a photo of Onodera's crush?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I shouldn't look at it...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, of course I can't look at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's totally wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your patience!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought us some tea—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, thanks! I really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have some time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to talk about something?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play a word-chain game?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Onodera?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold up! It's still too early for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you do when you've completely run out of things to talk about!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a graveyard where conversations go to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you're right. Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.51,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess suddenly being thrown into such a situation is pretty nerve-wracking.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I wouldn't have any problem talking to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.65,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! Onodera's struggling just as much as I am!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gotta man up and find the right topic...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.79,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have your yearbook from junior high, maybe?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.64,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be the most surefire topic of them all, but hey, at least it'll get the conversation going.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! This really brings back memories, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just six months ago, we were junior high students.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you call this feeling.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball game tournament when we were first-years!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I got to be friends with Ruri-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I have been in the same class since we were second-years.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.78,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it wasn't till the third year that we actually started talking...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.60,0:17:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's Onodera again. Man, even as a junior high student she was adorable.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, here she is again...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gotta give myself props!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.25,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how tiny she is, I can always spot Onodera.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess that makes me a little happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.04,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in any of these photos, am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. See, here you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And here... and here...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are again!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and look, there you are again!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Onodera.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.66,0:18:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you spotted such tiny images!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because you stand out, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you were popular with the girls, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No I wasn't! If anyone was popular, it was you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me, by a long shot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're really nice, Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It just might be that you haven't realized it yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.79,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in junior high,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.42,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew at least one girl who had a crush on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Who was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just say that and not tell me! That's not fair, Onodera!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already graduated, so it doesn't matter, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling! Not unless that girl gives me permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you meet Maiko-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, we actually go way back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't been able to get rid of each other since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.68,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, actually, talking to Onodera is really fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.19,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only this moment could last forever and ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Onodera?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped raining.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Typhoon No. 16 has swerved way off its original course,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}and is now heading towards the sea to the east.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}God damn it! Curse you, typhoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.34,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't you take a hint at all? Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.49,0:19:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, then I'll be heading home after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't right for a guy and a girl to spend the night alone in a house.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! I want to spend the night!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to talk with her some more!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.52,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Onodera... Aren't you gonna stop me from going?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be kind of weird for you to stay when it's stopped raining.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course it is. You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.78,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course it's weird. I knew it all along! I not crying over it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.48,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for today. I had such a great time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so did I.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder... when I'll get to see her next.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That part-time job was only for today,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it's still summer vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come to think of it, you and I...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We talk a lot at school, but now that I think about it, we don't—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, Raku!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.67,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,—know each other's e-mail addresses, do we?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Now that you mention it, we don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we exchange them now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, I'm going to set up the infrared.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.81,0:20:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-All right! Sure you don't mind, Onodera? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so happy that I built up the courage to ask!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I sent it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never expected Ichijou-kun to ask me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That makes me happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things have been going so great today, divine punishment could be waiting for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had such a good time today.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When will I get to see him again?
