Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.49,0:21:38.86,Sign3,,0,0,0,,{\b0\fs25\an4\blur0.6\fscx527.28\fscy527.28\c&H181818&\pos(248,282)}It w{\alpha&HFF&}as me.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.86,0:21:39.11,Sign3,,0,0,0,,{\b0\fs25\an4\blur0.6\fscx527.28\fscy527.28\c&H181818&\pos(248,282)}It {\alpha&HFF&}was me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just... kidding...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, see you later, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.20,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Call me anytime you need my help again!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.85,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nearly two years after we met, I finally got her e-mail address!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So freakin' happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.14,Sign2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\c&H504140&\fscx119\fscy119\1a&H00&\pos(659.223,26.666)}New Message
