Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would it be too shameless to send her a text right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.26,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it should be okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.43,0:22:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure we both had a blast talking, and I want to keep talking to her more than anything right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.86,0:22:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right! Sent!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.83,0:22:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here it comes!
