Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.03,0:22:21.28,Sign2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an7\fscx150\fscy150\c&H4A4343&\pos(345,512)}I enjoyed it too.\N Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.49,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.28,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night? Is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.18,0:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that us having a blast was just my imagination!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no way...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After all... Th-That...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did great today, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan might even praise me.
